{"tid":1571512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地幾時先會明？！而家係戰爭狀態？！","createTime":"2019-09-15T12:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T13:47:42.000Z","uid":166734,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"745bf3158833d11df7f125598cfc891b5113e250","tid":1571512,"uid":166734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"我求下大家諗清楚呢場仗！ 係真係戰爭黎架！<br />\n<br />\n而家出得黎已經唔係遊行,係上戰場，仲要係一個無得走既戰場。你去得就唔係全身而退，而係用最小既兵力達到目的。 而家唔係防守保衛戰，而家主攻奪權戰。<br />\n<br />\n亦唔使再批判黑警執法，而家係得2個陣營。佢地只會幫佢既陣營。呢班係武警，香港警察無左架啦。<br />\n<br />\n再諗住出黎嘉年華既，你地可以直接做返你地地區工作。戰場唔岩你地。<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足早有覺悟。不過我地好快消磨掉。<br />\n<br />\n全民勇武 在所難免"},{"pid":"d7be79ea1d9367f8475aa715d872af24ff7c01b6","tid":1571512,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXecFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=33015c8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXecFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=06be7440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"d42185e4172bfddeb3f48a654354d5823638e6ee","tid":1571512,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:42:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span> <br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"9d8aa3852e277aa56e2c38d697b7e3a3df578c3e","tid":1571512,"uid":166734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:43:20.000Z","msg":"求下你地了解清楚而家唔再係以前既遊行啦！！"},{"pid":"